Neandrathal Pime steps out of the stasis pod he was in. He looked at his new beast mode which was a Prehistoric Human. He opened up his com link. "Greetings fellow Maximals. I am Neandrathal Prime. I have come to join you. Please come and pick me up." 
After that he sat down beside a tree and waited.
